    <item>
      <title>Maintenance Log - Tenth Week: Frontend Auth, Routing, and API Client Structure</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-tenthweek/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>cph-ja472@stud.ek.dk (Jesper Andersen)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-tenthweek/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Devlog Week 10: Frontend Auth, Routing, and API Client Structure&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;devlog-week-10-frontend-auth-routing-and-api-client-structure&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#devlog-week-10-frontend-auth-routing-and-api-client-structure&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This entry covers the &amp;ldquo;plumbing&amp;rdquo; for the React frontend: the route layout, guarded routes by role, auth rehydration, and an API layer split by domain.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What Changed&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;what-changed&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#what-changed&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Vite + React + React Router setup with a domain-organized structure (&lt;code&gt;pages/&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;components/&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;utils/&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;context/&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;styles/&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Declarative nested routing with a layout route and &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;Outlet /&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Auth context for user state, token rehydration, and role checks&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;ProtectedRoute&lt;/code&gt; component for nestable route protection&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;API layer split by domain with a shared &lt;code&gt;apiRequest()&lt;/code&gt; helper&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Routing: Nested Layout + Guards&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;routing-nested-layout--guards&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#routing-nested-layout--guards&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The router is set up as nested routes:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Maintenance Log - Ninth Week: React Frontend Kickoff (Vite, Routing, Layout)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-ninthweek/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>cph-ja472@stud.ek.dk (Jesper Andersen)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/Portfolio/devlog/maintenancelog-ninthweek/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Devlog Week 9: React Frontend Kickoff (Vite, Routing, Layout)&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;devlog-week-9-react-frontend-kickoff-vite-routing-layout&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#devlog-week-9-react-frontend-kickoff-vite-routing-layout&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This week starts the frontend phase of the Maintenance Log project. The focus was not new domain functionality yet, but establishing a clean React baseline: routing, layout composition, reusable UI building blocks, and a consistent styling foundation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
